&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For him, each sufferer was more than ___(8)___ a case that was to be cured&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating&amp;nbsp;thinking of Pasteur on sufferers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
