&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;For him, each sufferer was more than &lt;strong&gt;just&lt;/strong&gt; a case that was to be cured&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;But&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is&amp;nbsp;used &lt;strong&gt;for introducing an idea that contrasts with or is different from what has just been said&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(किंतु, परंतु, लेकिन)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Absolutely&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;completely; totally&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(पूरी तरह से; सर्वथा; संपूर्ण रूप से)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Exactly&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;in exact terms; without vagueness&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(सटीक शब्दों में; अस्पष्टता के बिना)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;For him, each sufferer was more than ___(8)___ a case that was to be cured&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;पीड़ितों पर पाश्चर की सोच का संकेत दे रहा है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य में &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; शब्द का प्रयोग &lt;strong&gt;किसी बीमारी, चोट या समस्या के उदाहरण को इंगित करता है&lt;/strong&gt;।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान में भरने के लिए सबसे उपयुक्त शब्द&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;just&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Just&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ&amp;nbsp;है केवल।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;An entrepreneur is more than&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;just&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;a risk-taker&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 3 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;For him, each sufferer was more than&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;just&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;a case that was to be cured&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;fight&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;He looked upon the ___(9)___ against hydrophobia as a battle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating doing something against hydrophobia as a battle&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The use of the&amp;nbsp;word &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;battle&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicates&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a lengthy and difficult conflict or struggle&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;fight&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;fight&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means &lt;strong&gt;to try very hard to stop or prevent something&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Scientists are claiming a major breakthrough in the &lt;strong&gt;fight&lt;/strong&gt; against cancer&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the &lt;strong&gt;fight&lt;/strong&gt; against hydrophobia as a battle...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Scuffle&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a short, not very violent fight&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(हाथापाई, हाथाबाँही, झिड़प)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Mutiny&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;refusing to obey the orders of a person in authority&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(विद्रोह होना या करना)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Rivalry&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;competition between people, groups, etc&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(प्रतिद्वंद्वित, प्रतिस्&amp;zwj;पर्धा)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;He looked upon the ___(9)___ against hydrophobia as a battle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;एक लड़ाई के रूप में हाइड्रोफोबिया के खिलाफ कुछ करने का संकेत दे रहा है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य में &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;battle&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;शब्द का प्रयोग,&amp;nbsp;एक लंबा और कठिन संघर्ष, का संकेत करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान में भरने के लिए सबसे उपयुक्त शब्द&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;fight&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Fight&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ&amp;nbsp;है &lt;strong&gt;कुछ रोकने का ज़ोरदार प्रयास करना&lt;/strong&gt;।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Scientists are claiming a major breakthrough in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;fight&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;against cancer&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 1 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;fight&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;against hydrophobia as a battle...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;determined&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the fight against hydrophobia as a battle and he was ___(10)___ to win at any cost&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating how Pasteur stood&amp;nbsp;against hydrophobia&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The use of the&amp;nbsp;word &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;win&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicates&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to get something by hard work, great effort, etc&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;determined&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;determined&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;having firmly decided to do something or to succeed, even if it is difficult&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;The government is &lt;strong&gt;determined &lt;/strong&gt;to tackle inflation&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the fight against hydrophobia as a battle and he was&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;determined&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to win at any cost&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Devised&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to invent a new way of doing something&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(कुछ करने का नया तरीक़ा निकालना)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Decided&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;clear; definite&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(स्&amp;zwj;पष्&amp;zwj;ट; निश्चित)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Developed&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;of a good level or standard&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(विकसित, उन्&amp;zwj;नत)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the fight against hydrophobia as a battle and he was ___(10)___ to win at any cost&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;यह दर्शाता है कि पाश्चर हाइड्रोफोबिया के खिलाफ कैसे खड़ा था।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य में &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;win&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; शब्द का प्रयोग &lt;strong&gt;कठिन परिश्रम, महान प्रयास आदि से कुछ पाने की ओर संकेत करता है&lt;/strong&gt;।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान में भरने के लिए सबसे उपयुक्त शब्द&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;determined&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Determined&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ&amp;nbsp;है &lt;strong&gt;कठिन होने के बावजूद किसी काम में सफलता प्राप्त करने का संकल्प, कृतसंकल्&amp;zwj;प, दृढ़निश्&amp;zwj;चयी&lt;/strong&gt;।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The government is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;determined&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to tackle inflation&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
