&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He looked upon the fight against hydrophobia as a battle and he was &lt;strong&gt;determined&lt;/strong&gt; to win at any cost&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;who&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I was walking home from work when I saw someone ___(1)___ I thought was my friend Sandra&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating identifying someone like my friend Sandra&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;who&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;who&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is&amp;nbsp;used &lt;strong&gt;for saying exactly which person or what kind of person you are talking about&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
