&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;lsquo;Make in India&amp;rsquo; is a call to the global manufacturers aimed at making India a manufacturing ___(2)___&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;to make something in large quantities using machines in India&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The use of the&amp;nbsp;word &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;manufacturing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicates&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the making of articles on a large scale using machinery; industrial production&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;hub&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;hub&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the central and most important part of a place or an activity&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
