		&lt;li&gt;The preposition&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;at&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;used &lt;strong&gt;to show where somebody or something is or where something happens&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The preposition&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;to&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;used &lt;strong&gt;for showing the purpose of an action&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
