&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Conclusion:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;भारत में निवेश को आसान बनाने के लिए बनाया गया एक राष्ट्रीय कार्यक्रम।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 3 है&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पुरा वाक्य&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;It is a national program designed&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;facilitate investment...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;development&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill ___4___​&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;enhance something related to skill&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The use of the&amp;nbsp;word &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;enhance&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicates&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to improve something or to make something look better&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;development&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;development&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means &lt;strong&gt;the process of becoming bigger, stronger, better etc&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;development&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of this industry will take several years&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 4&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;​...&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Agreement&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the state of agreeing with somebody or something&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(किसी बात या व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति से सहमति)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Progress&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means &lt;strong&gt;a&amp;nbsp;change or improvement&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(परिवर्तन या सुधार)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Decline&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a process or period of becoming weaker, smaller&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(अशक्त और क्षीण होने की प्रक्रिया या अवधि)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill ___4___​...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;कौशल से संबंधित कुछ बढ़ाने का संकेत दे रहा है।।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य में &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;enhance&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का प्रयोग &lt;strong&gt;कुछ सुधार करने या कुछ बेहतर दिखने का संकेत देता है&lt;/strong&gt;।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान में भरने के लिए सबसे उपयुक्त शब्द&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;development&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Development&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ&amp;nbsp;है &lt;strong&gt;अधिक विस्&amp;zwj;तृत, सुदृढ़, बेहतर आदि होने या बनाने की प्रक्रिया, विकसित होने या करने की प्रक्रिया&lt;/strong&gt;।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;development&lt;/strong&gt; of this industry will take several years&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 4 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;​...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is a national program designed to&amp;nbsp;facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill development and build best-in-class manufacturing ___(5)___&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicating&amp;nbsp;to develop or to manufacture something&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The use of the&amp;nbsp;word &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;manufacturing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indicates&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;making something in large quantities using machines&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;infrastructure&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the basic systems and services that are necessary for a country or an organization&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Much of the state-owned industrial&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is beyond repair&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill development and build best-in-class manufacturing &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Groundwork&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;work that is done in preparation for further work or study&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(उच्&amp;zwj;चतर अध्&amp;zwj;ययन के लिए की गई आरंभिक तैयारी)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Fundamental&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;basic and important; from which everything else develops&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(बुनियादी और महत्वपूर्ण; मूल स्रोत से संबंधित)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Footing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the level or position of somebody/something in relation to somebody or something else&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(किसी व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति या वस्&amp;zwj;तु का स्&amp;zwj;तर या पद अन्&amp;zwj;य व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति या वस्&amp;zwj;तु की तुलना में)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;It is a national program designed to&amp;nbsp;facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill development and build best-in-class manufacturing ___(5)___&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;कुछ विकसित करने या निर्माण करने का संकेत दे रहा है।।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य में &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;manufacturing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; शब्द का प्रयोग &lt;strong&gt;मशीनों का उपयोग करके बड़ी मात्रा में कुछ बनाने का संकेत देता है&lt;/strong&gt;।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान में भरने के लिए सबसे उपयुक्त शब्द&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ&amp;nbsp;है &lt;strong&gt;किसी देश या संगठन के लिए अपेक्षित आधारभूत प्रणालियाँ और सेवाएँ&lt;/strong&gt;।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Much of the state-owned industrial &lt;strong&gt;infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt; is beyond repair&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 1 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;It is a national program designed to facilitate investment, foster innovation, enhance skill development and build best-in-class manufacturing&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Has someone verified all the bills?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Active Voice&lt;/span&gt;, a sentence emphasizes the subject,&amp;nbsp;performing an action.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Passive Voice&lt;/span&gt;, a sentence emphasizes the action or the object of the sentence.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;given sentence&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is in&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;passive voice&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and it is in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;When we convert this sentence into an&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;active voice&lt;/span&gt;, the subject &amp;#39;&lt;b&gt;all the bills&lt;/b&gt;&amp;#39; of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;passive&amp;nbsp;voice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;becomes the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;object&lt;/span&gt;, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;object&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;someone&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; becomes the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;subject&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The passive format &amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;have + been + V3 (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;verified&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot; should be&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;converted into&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the active format &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;has +&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;V3 (verified)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;active and passive voice&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;rule&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Hence, the correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Verbs of passive format have a different set of tenses (*V3 - Past participle or Third form of the Verb) as given below in the table:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 330px;&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
	&lt;colgroup&gt;
		&lt;col width=&quot;183&quot; /&gt;
		&lt;col width=&quot;221&quot; /&gt;
		&lt;col width=&quot;156&quot; /&gt;
		&lt;col width=&quot;246&quot; /&gt;
	&lt;/colgroup&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;           TENSE&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;TENSE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;            ACTIVE&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;ACTIVE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;          PASSIVE&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;PASSIVE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;      PASSIVE CONVERSION&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;PASSIVE CONVERSION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
