&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;professional&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Amateur&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;a person who does not have skill or experience when doing something&lt;/span&gt;. (आवश्&amp;zwj;यक कौशल या अनुभव के बिना काम करने वाला व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;amateur&lt;/strong&gt; pianist made one or two false starts before finally playing the piece right through from the beginning&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;​Let&amp;#39;s see the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;meaning&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of other given options:-
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Apprentice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a person who works for low pay, in order to learn the skills needed in a particular job&lt;/strong&gt;. (हुनर-विशेष सीखने के लिए कम वेतन पर काम करने को तैयार व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति; प्रशिक्षार्थी)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;My son is an &lt;strong&gt;apprentice&lt;/strong&gt; in a furniture maker&amp;#39;s workshop&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Novice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a person who is new and without experience in a certain job, situation, etc&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(किसी विशेष काम, परिसि्&amp;zwj;थति आदि के लिए नया और अनुभवहीन व्यक्ति; नौसिखिया)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Novice&lt;/strong&gt; programmers sometimes make fundamental errors&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Professional&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a person who has a lot of skill and experience&lt;/strong&gt;. (अति निपुण या अनुभवी व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;She wants to become a &lt;strong&gt;professional &lt;/strong&gt;cook&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Learner&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;a person who is learning&lt;/strong&gt;. (जो अभी सीख रहा है या ज्ञान प्राप्&amp;zwj;त कर रहा है; शिक्षार्थी)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;She was a quick &lt;strong&gt;learner&lt;/strong&gt;, and her German got better by the day&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;antonyms&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Amateur&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;professional&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;, master,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;expert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;synonyms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Amateur&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;inexperienced, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;unprofessional, unskilled&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;DACB&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;independent&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of any other sentence as it is giving general information about&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;what the wild elephant does on entering the outskirts of a town&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;. Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;first part&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what the elephant does when it went to the main road&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what happened with the people who were standing on the main road&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;B&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;concluding&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;part&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;where and how did the elephant finally entered&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Paragraph after rearranging the sentences&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The wild elephant first reached the outskirts of our town, breaking down fences like matchsticks.&amp;nbsp;It then came to the main road and smashed all the stalls selling fruits, mud pots, and clothes.&amp;nbsp;The people on the main road ran helter-skelter in panic.&amp;nbsp;Finally, the elephant entered a school ground, breaking through the brick wall.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hint-text-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hint&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Rules to Solve the Para Jumbles&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Read the sentences&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;attentively and try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;comprehend the idea or theme of the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;eliminate the irrelevant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the opening&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(independent sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and closing sentences&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(concluding sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the mandatory pairs&lt;/span&gt;. Two sentences can be connected through various connectors and other determinants.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;D&amp;#39; किसी अन्य वाक्य से स्वतंत्र है क्योंकि यह&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;एक शहर के बाहरी इलाके में प्रवेश करने पर एक जंगली हाथी क्या करता है&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;के बारे में सामान्य जानकारी दे रहा है। अतः &amp;#39;D&amp;#39; पहला भाग है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य A, D के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि हाथी मुख्य सड़क पर जाने पर क्या करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य C, A के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि मुख्य सड़क पर खड़े लोगों के साथ क्या हुआ।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;B&amp;#39; अंतिम भाग है क्योंकि यह बताता है कि हाथी आखिर में कहाँ और कैसे प्रवेश करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ACEBDF&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;independent&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of any other sentence as it is giving general information about&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Timothy, the tiger cub&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot;. Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;first part&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;the description of the tiger cub spotted by the grandfather&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;E&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;the reaction of the cub when spotted by the grandfather&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;B&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;E&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what did the grandfather do with the cub&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;B&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;the initial diet given by the grandfather to the cub&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;concluding&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;part&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;the diet followed by the cub later on&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Paragraph after rearranging the sentences&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Timothy, the tiger cub was discovered by Grandfather in the Terai jungle near Dehra.&amp;nbsp;One day when Grandfather was strolling in the jungle, he spotted a little tiger about 18 inches long.&amp;nbsp;The frightened animal was hiding among the intricate roots of a banyan tree.&amp;nbsp;Grandfather picked him and brought him home.&amp;nbsp;The tiger cub was named Timothy by Grandfather and initially brought up entirely on milk.&amp;nbsp;Later, he was put on a diet of raw mutton and cod liver oil.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hint-text-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hint&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Rules to Solve the Para Jumbles&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Read the sentences&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;attentively and try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;comprehend the idea or theme of the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;eliminate the irrelevant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the opening&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(independent sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and closing sentences&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(concluding sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the mandatory pairs&lt;/span&gt;. Two sentences can be connected through various connectors and other determinants.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;A&amp;#39; किसी अन्य वाक्य से स्वतंत्र है क्योंकि यह&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;बाघ शावक टिमोथी&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;के बारे में सामान्य जानकारी दे रहा है। अतः &amp;#39;A&amp;#39; पहला भाग है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य C, A के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह दादा द्वारा देखे गए बाघ के शावक का विवरण बताता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य E, C के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह दादा द्वारा देखे जाने पर शावक की प्रतिक्रिया की व्याख्या करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य B, E के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि दादा ने शावक के साथ क्या किया।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य D, B के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह दादा द्वारा शावक को दिए गए प्रारंभिक आहार की व्याख्या करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;F&amp;#39; अंतिम भाग है क्योंकि यह बाद में शावक द्वारा पालन किए जाने वाले आहार की व्याख्या करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;ADECBF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;independent&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of any other sentence as it is giving general information about&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;a singer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Mukandan Misra and his wife&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;. Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;first part&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;the habit of the only child of the couple&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;E&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what did the child often used to do&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;E&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;one day what happened in that forest where the child used to run away&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;B&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;what the disciples did when felt tired&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;concluding&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;part&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;because it explains &lt;b&gt;what Tansen has done with his disciples&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Paragraph after rearranging the sentences&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;A singer called Mukandan Misra and his wife lived in Behat near Gwalior.&amp;nbsp;Tansen, their only child was very naughty.&amp;nbsp;Often he would run away to the woods and soon learned to imitate the calls of birds and animals.&amp;nbsp;Once Swami Haridas was traveling through the forest with his disciples.&amp;nbsp;Tired, the group settled down to rest in a shady grove.&amp;nbsp;Tansen thought it would be fun to frighten the resting men with the roar of a tiger.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hint-text-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hint&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Rules to Solve the Para Jumbles&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Read the sentences&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;attentively and try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;comprehend the idea or theme of the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;eliminate the irrelevant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the opening&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(independent sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and closing sentences&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(concluding sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the mandatory pairs&lt;/span&gt;. Two sentences can be connected through various connectors and other determinants.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;A&amp;#39; किसी अन्य वाक्य से स्वतंत्र है क्योंकि यह&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;एक गायक मुकंदन मिश्रा और उनकी पत्नी&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;के बारे में सामान्य जानकारी दे रहा है। अतः &amp;#39;A&amp;#39; पहला भाग है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य D, A के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह मुकंदन मिश्रा और उनकी पत्नी की इकलौती संतान की आदत की व्याख्या करता है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य E, D के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि बच्चा अक्सर क्या करता था।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य C, E&amp;nbsp;के बाद आएगा&amp;nbsp;क्योंकि यह बताता है कि एक दिन उस जंगल में क्या हुआ जहां बच्चा भागता था।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य B, C के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि शिष्यों ने थकान महसूस होने पर क्या किया।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;F&amp;#39; अंतिम भाग है क्योंकि यह बताता है कि तानसेन ने अपने शिष्यों के साथ क्या किया है।&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;He said that Manan had come to college the previous day&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;given sentence&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;direct speech&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;basic rules&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for changing or&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;converting direct speech into indirect speech:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;commas, inverted commas&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;removed&lt;/span&gt;, and&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;that&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt; added, &amp;#39;yesterday&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;becomes&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;the previous day&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;past simple tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;V&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;(came)&amp;nbsp;+ Object&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will be changed into&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;past&amp;nbsp;perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ had + V&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(come)&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 2&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/confusion-points-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Confusion Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;You may think that &lt;strong&gt;option 3&lt;/strong&gt; should be correct but&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;yesterday&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;has to be changed into the &amp;#39;&amp;#39;previous day&amp;#39;&amp;#39; in the indirect speech.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Thus, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 2&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The following table will enable us to know how tense changes into Indirect speech:-
	&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;width: 0px; border: none;&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
		&lt;colgroup&gt;
			&lt;col width=&quot;422&quot; /&gt;
