&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;direct speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Direct speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;को&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;indirect speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;में बदलने या बदलने के लिए बुनियादी नियम:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Commas, inverted commas&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;हटा दिए जाते हैं।&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Reporting verb &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;said to&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; बन जाती है &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;asked&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39; और question mark&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(?)&lt;/span&gt; पूर्ण विराम &lt;strong&gt;(.)&lt;/strong&gt; बन जाता है।&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The first-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;I&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;, third-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;he&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; बन जाता है और second-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;you&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;, the first-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;me&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; बन जाता है।&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Present simple tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Subject&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;V&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(can)&amp;nbsp;+ Object&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;को&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;past&amp;nbsp;simple tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ V&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; position: relative; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;(could)&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;में बदल दिया जाएगा।&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 1 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;why his low score&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;i.e.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;this part of the sentence&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;has an error&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the given sentence, the use of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adverb &amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;incorrect&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adverb &amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;for what reason or purpose&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;preposition &amp;#39;for&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;should be used&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;in place of&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adverb&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;preposition &amp;#39;for&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; is used &lt;strong&gt;after nouns such as &amp;#39;reason&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;or &amp;#39;cause&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;or&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;for talking about reasons or causes&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Correct Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He wanted to know the reason &lt;strong&gt;for his low score&lt;/strong&gt; in Mathematics&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिए गए वाक्य में &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adverb &amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; का प्रयोग गलत है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Adverb &amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; का अर्थ &lt;strong&gt;किस कारण या उद्देश्य &lt;/strong&gt;से है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;adverb&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;why&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; के स्थान पर &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;preposition &amp;#39;for&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; का प्रयोग किया जाना चाहिए।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Preposition &amp;#39;for&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; का प्रयोग &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;nouns&lt;/span&gt; जैसे &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;reason&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; या &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;cause&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; के बाद या &lt;strong&gt;कारणों&amp;nbsp;के बारे में बात करने के लिए&lt;/strong&gt; किया जाता है।&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अतः सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;सही वाक्य:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;He wanted to know the reason&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;for his low score&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;in Mathematics&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;much&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence talking about &lt;strong&gt;someone&amp;#39;s level of poverty&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate word to be filled in the blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;much&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;much&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means &lt;strong&gt;very&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;This command has a &lt;strong&gt;much&lt;/strong&gt; richer set of options and arguments than a lookup function&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Much&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; is often used with &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;comparative&lt;/strong&gt; adjectives and adverbs&lt;/em&gt;: &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;much older, much faster.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We can use&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;much&amp;#39; before comparative&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;adjectives and adverbs&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;to make a stronger comparison.&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Sometimes the prices in the local shop are &lt;strong&gt;much better &lt;/strong&gt;than the supermarket&amp;#39;s prices.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He is &lt;strong&gt;much&lt;/strong&gt; poorer than all his friends&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;us&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;the other&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Most&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;greatest in number or amount&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(संख्&amp;zwj;या या मात्रा में&amp;nbsp;अधिकतम)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;More&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to a greater degree than usual or than something else&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(सामान्&amp;zwj;य या अन्&amp;zwj;य से अपेक्षाकृत अधिक)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Very&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;extremely; in a high degree&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(अत्&amp;zwj;यधिक, बहुत; बड़ी मात्रा में)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &lt;strong&gt;किसी के गरीबी के स्तर&lt;/strong&gt; के बारे में बात कर रहा है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;इसलिए, रिक्त स्थान की पूर्ति के लिए सर्वाधिक उपयुक्त शब्द &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;much&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Much&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; शब्द का अर्थ &lt;strong&gt;अत्&amp;zwj;यधिक&lt;/strong&gt; है।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;This command has a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;much&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;richer set of options and arguments than a&amp;nbsp;lookup function&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Much&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;अक्सर तुलनात्मक विशेषणों और क्रियाविशेषणों के साथ प्रयोग किया जाता है: &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;much older, much faster.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;हम तुलनात्मक विशेषणों और क्रियाविशेषणों से पहले &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;much&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; का उपयोग एक मजबूत तुलना करने के लिए कर सकते हैं।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;उदाहरण:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Sometimes the prices in the local shop are &lt;strong&gt;much better &lt;/strong&gt;than the supermarket&amp;#39;s prices.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 1 है&lt;/span&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;पूर्ण वाक्य:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;He is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;much&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;poorer than all his friends&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;relevent&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;i.e.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;this word is misspelled&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Let us&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;explore&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;:-

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Relevent&lt;/span&gt;: There is no such word in English or we can say that there is some spelling mistake in this word.

		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;correct&amp;nbsp;spelling is &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Relevant&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;and it means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;important and useful&lt;/strong&gt;. (महत्वपूर्ण और उपयोगी)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Distinct&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;clearly different&lt;/strong&gt;. (स्&amp;zwj;पष्&amp;zwj;टतया भिन्&amp;zwj;न)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Beseech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to ask somebody for something in a worried way because you want or need it very much&lt;/strong&gt;. (अनुनय करना, विनती करना, विनतीपूर्वक मांगना)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Surrender&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to stop fighting and admit that you have lost&lt;/strong&gt;. (लड़ना बंद कर अपनी हार मान लेना, आत्&amp;zwj;मसमर्पण कर देना)&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Relevant&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;in a&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&amp;nbsp;sentence&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relevant&lt;/strong&gt; documents were presented in court&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;The manager said to the salesman, &amp;ldquo;Well done! Your performance has been exceptional.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;given sentence&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is an&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;direct speech&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;basic rules&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for changing or&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;converting indirect speech into direct speech:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;commas,&amp;nbsp;inverted commas&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;added&lt;/span&gt;, and&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;that&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;removed&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;lauded&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;replaced by &amp;#39;said to&amp;#39;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;said&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; is replaced by&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;exclamation &amp;#39;&amp;#39;well done!&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;third-person&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;pronoun &amp;#39;his&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will be changed into the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;second-person&amp;nbsp;pronoun&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Your&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;past perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ had + V3 (been)&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;Object&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will be changed into&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ has + V3 (been) +&amp;nbsp;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;From the following rules, we get the&amp;nbsp;correct sentence&amp;nbsp;as&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 4&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The following table will enable us to know how tense changes&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;into Indirect speech&lt;/span&gt;:

	&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;width: 0px; border: none;&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
		&lt;colgroup&gt;
			&lt;col width=&quot;422&quot; /&gt;
			&lt;col width=&quot;445&quot; /&gt;
		&lt;/colgroup&gt;
		&lt;tbody&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 21px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Direct Speech&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Direct Speech&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Indirect Speech&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Indirect Speech&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 27px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Present simple  (Subject +V1st + Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Present simple (Subject +V1st + Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past simple (Subject +V2 + Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past simple (Subject +V2 + Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 28px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Present continuous (Subject +is/am/are+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Present continuous (Subject +is/am/are+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past Continuous (Subject +was/were+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past Continuous (Subject +was/were+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 27px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Present perfect (Subject + has/have+V3+Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Present perfect (Subject + has/have+V3+Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past perfect (Subject+had+V3+Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past perfect (Subject+had+V3+Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 25px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past simple (Subject+V2+Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past simple (Subject+V2+Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past perfect (Subject+had+V3+Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past perfect (Subject+had+V3+Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 27px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past Continuous (Subject +was/were+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past Continuous (Subject +was/were+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Past perfect continuous (Subject +had been+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Past perfect continuous (Subject +had been+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 26px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Future simple (Subject+ will/shall+V1+object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Future simple (Subject+ will/shall+V1+object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Present Conditional (Subject+ would+V1+object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Present Conditional (Subject+ would+V1+object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 29px;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Future Continuous (Subject +will/shall+be+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Future Continuous (Subject +will/shall+be+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
				&lt;td data-sheets-value=&quot;{&amp;quot;1&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Conditional Continuous (Subject +would+be+V1 +ing+ Object)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;padding: 2px 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Conditional Continuous (Subject +would+be+V1 +ing+ Object)&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;/tbody&gt;
	&lt;/table&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;दिया गया वाक्य &lt;strong&gt;in&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;direct speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Indirect speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;को&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;direct speech&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;में बदलने या बदलने के लिए बुनियादी नियम:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Commas, inverted commas&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;जोड़े जाते हैं,&amp;nbsp;और&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;that&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;हटा दिया जाता है,&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;lauded&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; को &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;said to&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; से बदल दिया जाता है, और &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;said&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; को &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;exclamation mark &amp;#39;&amp;#39;well done&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; से बदल दिया जाता है।&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Third-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;his&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;, second-person pronoun &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Your&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; बन जाता है।&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Past perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ had + V3 (been)&amp;nbsp;+&amp;nbsp;Object&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;को&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present perfect tense&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;format &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Subject&amp;nbsp;+ has + V3 (been) +&amp;nbsp;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;में बदल दिया जाएगा।&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अत: सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;विकल्प 4 &lt;/span&gt;है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;CABD&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;independent&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of any other sentence as it is giving general information about&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what was Jacob doing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot;. Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;first part&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what Jacob had found interesting in the book&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;B&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;will come after&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what Jacob could have done with the metal detector&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;concluding&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;part&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;because it explains&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;what Jacob&amp;nbsp;finally decided to do to buy a metal detector&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Paragraph after rearranging the sentences&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Jacob was reading one of his comic books when he came upon something interesting.&amp;nbsp;It was the advertisement for a metal detector called Wonder Sweeper 5000.&amp;nbsp;Jacob believed he could find the buried treasure of the pirates if he had that detector. So, he decided to save every penny till he had enough money to buy one&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hint-text-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hint&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Rules to Solve the Para Jumbles&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Read the sentences&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;attentively and try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;comprehend the idea or theme of the sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;eliminate the irrelevant&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;options.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the opening&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(independent sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and closing sentences&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(concluding sentence)&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Try to&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;identify the mandatory pairs&lt;/span&gt;. Two sentences can be connected through various connectors and other determinants.&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/hinglish-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Hinglish&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;C&amp;#39; किसी अन्य वाक्य से स्वतंत्र है क्योंकि यह &amp;quot;जैकब क्या कर रहा था&amp;quot; के बारे में सामान्य जानकारी दे रहा है। अतः &amp;#39;C&amp;#39; पहला भाग है।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य A, C के बाद आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि जैकब ने किताब में क्या दिलचस्प पाया था।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य B, A के बाद&amp;nbsp;आएगा क्योंकि यह बताता है कि जैकब मेटल डिटेक्टर के साथ क्या कर सकता था।&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;वाक्य &amp;#39;D&amp;#39; अंतिम भाग है क्योंकि यह बताता है कि जैकब ने आखिरकार मेटल डिटेक्टर खरीदने के लिए क्या करने का फैसला किया।&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;He is said to have lived on a liquid diet for years&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Active Voice&lt;/span&gt;, a sentence emphasizes the subject,&amp;nbsp;performing an action.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Passive Voice&lt;/span&gt;, a sentence emphasizes the action or the object of the sentence.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given sentence is in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;active voice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and it is in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present simple tense&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;When we convert this sentence into a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;passive voice&lt;/span&gt;, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;subject&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;People&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;active voice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;becomes the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;hidden object&lt;/span&gt;, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;object&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;he&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; becomes the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;subject&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;active format&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;V1&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;say&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot; should be&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;converted into&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;passive format&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;is + V3 (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;said&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;active and passive voice&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;rule&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;present simple tense&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Verbs of passive format have a different set of tenses (*V3 - Past participle or Third form of the Verb) as given below in the table:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

